listitem.para:
Attribute is used to represent an attribute value.  An attribute has a name and a (generically typed) value,
and may be marked as read-only.  Attribute values that are expensive to load (such as large binary data) may be lazy-loaded; 
the isLoaded() method may be used to determine whether the Attribute has been loaded or not.

